      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "This video has it all: a cheesy theme song, lots of lens flair, scratches in the film, low color saturation, and an intro where two riders are in some snowy mountains when everyone’s keyed up to see Daytona (there’s an explanation in a stuffy conference room, another odd choice). It’s all part of the flavor of this video, so enjoy the charm.",
            "type": "text",
